channel.title: [562][Release]Painzone Working construction, summoning and hunter too!
channel.description:
[IMG]http://kajzone.webs.com/painzone2.jpg[/img]
[b]EDIT! I have posted the location of the file where to change the login message at the bottom![/b]
Hi everyone, I know my name isn't popular on here but I've been lurking around for several years. I've coded and hosted many popular servers until I quit several years ago. I recently came back and looked into 562's I noticed that there are very little tuts on them so I thought I could help with releasing my server which is based on NRscape ( don't worry it took me ages to get all his racism and porn crap out but you'll barely recognize it, also fixed alot of his stupid bugs but I thanks Geo anyway for the basics that were in it, thanks Caelum and the maker of lightPkz too; etcetera etcetera. Some people started offering few 100€' for it they'll get it for free now. ( ps; kids don't pay money for private servers... You might need it later. )
-NO ANTI (b)LEACH- ( love that anime series :| ) :coolface:There's no virus or pc-disabling batch file in there.:trollface:
:eek: Before some random noobs start accusing me of most likely having a virus in it I'll say it like this: Learn using a computer with a unix os ( :penguin: not always linux ) And just code and host on there so you won't have to worry dipshizzle...
[ I'm not adding credits ( I thanks everyone who has worked on this server ) and don't want any rep or stuff... You don't have to post either I'm ok with just downloading, as you'll probably notice I don't give a beep about e-fame... doesn't feed my kids. ]
What painzone offers you:
[ul][*]:awesome: Started SoulWars. [*]:awesome: Godwars. [*]:awesome: PVP drops only from pk such as vesta's morrigans statius etc. [*]:awesome: Item on item, item on object, item on npc examples for new coders. just search the base. [*]:awesome: Anti flood ( thanks scootersam ) [*]:awesome: Had it run 3 days without a restart [*]:awesome: Most skills work ( You can hunt on several monsters and construction works with interfaces! ) [*]:awesome: A unique home same as on my never released 317 ' infinity ' [*]:awesome Lots of portals and npcs to take you somewhere to take out lots of commands. [*]:awesome: The world map button opens a map with teleport buttons [*]:awesome: Options, house button opens your house interfaces! [*]:awesome: Fully working canoe stations! ( I put one at the river at home ) [*]:awesome: You can hunt on rabbits, kebbits, birds and chinchompas using a knife on the first two gets you the best pking food there is! so hunter is a moneymaking skill the bird snare and box trap actually create the item and you have to click it to get your prey. Shaking box f.e. from the chins [*]:awesome: Farming based on geo's but added the drops from npc's [*]:awesome: I took out ::item and made the server work without spawning! [*]:awesome: An awesome economy server and 1600x xp per hit [*]:awesome: Free for all PK npc at home with interfaces [*]:awesome: Summoning works and so does the interface it's coded with the dismiss button and the face of your familiars you just have to add a button or a command to open the interface, I'm not spoonfeeding you guys. [*]:awesome: Alot of bosses, specials, trainingplaces etc [*]:awesome: You can't get dragon in shops from rune on everything gets dropped by boss npc's and other though guys! [*]:awesome: There is way more and I left some hidden eastereggs in there too for the people that'll use it they'll thank me alot.[/ul]
Some pictures but don't include all features:
[spoiler]
[img]http://kajzone.webs.com/home.png[/img]
[img]http://kajzone.webs.com/cons1.png[/img]
[img]http://kajzone.webs.com/cons2.png[/img]
[img]http://kajzone.webs.com/cons3.png[/img]
[img]http://kajzone.webs.com/home2.png[/img]
[img]http://kajzone.webs.com/familiars.png[/img]
[img]http://kajzone.webs.com/farming.png[/img]
[img]http://kajzone.webs.com/hunter.png[/img]
[/spoiler]
NOTE: the client still has my IP redirect in it but I'm no longer hosting so it's not advertising. If you want to change it search the client for:
[code]
painzone.serveftp.com and change it to your ip adress, don't know it?
go to www.ipchicken.com or use cmd, but I reckon if you don't know your ip you won't know how to use that.
[/code]
[b][size=10pt]Location of the "secret" .py files! (where to change the login message)[/size][/b]
[code] PainZone Server\PainZone 562\data\scripts\authentication.py [/code]
What to change: [code] # called when a player logs in def login(player): player.getActionSender().sendMessage("<shad=0066ff>Welcome to Painzone [562] Owner and coder is <img=1>Zero<img=1>"); return
# called when a player logs out def logout(player): pass [/code] Note that the files in the scripts map aren't java don't mess too much with them. I'm surprised people considered this as an anti leech..
[SIZE="7"]DOWNLOADS:[/SIZE] server: [url=http://www.megaupload.com/?d=WGYSAJXL]http://www.megaupload.com/?d=WGYSAJXL[/url] [url=http://uppit.com/cyzs3p9krxo1/PainZone_Server.rar]http://uppit.com/cyzs3p9krxo1/PainZone_Server.rar[/url] client: [url=http://uppit.com/2zschswa8qwd/PainZone.rar]http://uppit.com/2zschswa8qwd/PainZone.rar[/url]
